Articles.Content: I'm trying to upload something to the Spaceport, and it keeps spitting back an "errors" message. It doesn't tell me WHAT the errors are so that I can fix them. Any I deas as to what are typical errors, or how to finish the upload?
Double check it anytime you get an error. Most of the time it will upload regardless of the error.
What's the usual lag from hitting upload to appearing on the site?
